prodNameC: "鐳定"黃體脂酮放射免疫分析試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Progesterone Maia Tracer：contains I-125 labeled Progesterone derivative in 12.5ml
Phosphate-citrate buffer with bovine serum albumin.
Progesterone Maia Calibrators：contain respectively：0-0.15-0.5-1.5-5-15-50 ng/ml (0-0.477-1.59-4.77-15.9-47.7-159 nmol/l) of progesterone in human and horse serum matrix buffered with tris <0.1%w/w.1 ml for the zero standard,0.5 ml for each of the remaining standards.
Progesterone Maia Separation Reagent：contains goat anti-rabbit gammaglobulin coupled to magnetic particles in tris buffer with bovine serum albumin.
Progesterone Maia Antiserum：contains rabbit anti-progesterone in aqueous solution with rabbit gammaglobulins, bovine serum albumin.
Serotest S：The vial contains lyophilized control serum containing human serum.

efficacy: 定量檢測人體血清或血漿中黃體脂酮的含量。
